title: Jessie James Decker on the Perfect Gift for Mom-to-be!
description:
Country singer, entrepreneur and mom Jessie James Decker shares why BellyBuds by WavHello make the perfect Mother's Day gift for mom-to-be! Jessie and her husband Eric Decker used BellyBuds to play music, special voice messages and bond with their son while he was in the womb.

BellyBuds are special speakers for your baby bump that gently adhere to your belly and safely play music and voice messages to to the womb!
